question: Tōa-chiúⁿ ê 'sòaⁿ-tâi lia̍k-sûn chòe-chòe-chòe' tùi 2003 kàu 2005 ê kái-piàn cháiⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Sòaⁿ-tâi lia̍k-sûn chòe-chòe-chòe ê chu-liāu piáu-hiān chi̍t ê chè-tōaⁿ ê hā-chhiúⁿ-sè, chí-chā kim-liōng ê kái-chìn. Lia̍k-sûn tùi 2003 nî ê $325,321 kiám-chió kàu 2004 nî ê $247,587, koh chài kiám-chió kàu 2005 nî ê $171,590.

question: Na-niat-nî ê sî-chūn, 'pro-forma bōe-tit-chiūnn bōe-tit-lō·' kap 'chèng-siāu chòe-chòe bōe-tit-chiūnn bōe-tit-lō·' ê sûn-chiàⁿ-sòe kî-kan ê chha-ê-sòe siōng tōa?
Kohlai sann-go̍k ê sî-kan, lóng-chóng ū siâⁿ-chē ê 'stock-based employee compensation expense' hō͘ ka-thiⁿ?

Tī chiah-ê nî-tō͘ ê chòe-sió 'chòe-sò͘ kap liû-chúi-sèng hū-chè-sò͘ chòe-pò͘-lō͘' hā, chòe-thé 'sī-jī-chòe chòe-sò͘' kap chòe-thé 'chòe-pò͘-lō͘ ê chòe-sò͘' ê pí-lu̍t sī siáⁿ-chóng? Hō͘-sò͘ kàu siáⁿ-chóng? Tē-sann ūi siâu-siâu.
Jit sia hō͘ 'total stock-based employee compensation expense determined under fair value based method' ê siūⁿ-tāi hō͘-siong ki-suan chha-chōe koh-khah tuā hō͘ $25,000 ê nî-hūn ū kúi-ê?

Tī 2004 nî, chiūnnóng ê 'pro-forma net loss' chiap-sut ê 'total stock-based employee compensation expense' thik-beh chiap-tsò toā-sió ê phah-sò͘ ê cha̍p-hun-chi-la̍k? Chioh hō͘ lán kài-sǹg kàu sió-sò͘ ē ē-kha nn̄g ūi.
Nā-sī 'stock-based employee compensation expense' siâng-ka tī 2005 ê sî, nā-sī ē-iâⁿ 50% koh-khah kē, hit tang ê sin ê 'pro-forma net loss' ē sī siáⁿ-mih?
Sím-mi̍h hù-ka ia̍h-sī kiám-siàu ê tiâu-bo̍k ('hù-ka' ia̍h-sī 'kiám-siàu') chiap-koaⁿ hit-ê nî-tiâu ê phiah-lē piàn-tōa siōng-kài cheng-chháu, kap tī siáⁿ nn̄g tang chi-kan thêng-seng?
answer: Hit ê 'hù-ka: kó͘-chek kái-thiam chhiúⁿ-la̍t chiàⁿ-thâu chiàⁿ-tóe tháⁿ hū-hūn ê sîn-chè ki-sóan chha-tí siòng hū-hūn chiàⁿ-tóe tháⁿ ki-sóan chha-tí chiàⁿ-tóe' tiâu-bo̍k thêng-seng siōng-kài cheng-chháu. I tùi $2,297 (2004 nî) cheng-ka kàu $7,104 (2005 nî), cheng-ka liáu chē-chē 209% í-siōng, che piáu-sī chē-chē chha-tí ê nî-tóe piàn-tōa pí kah phiah-lē koân-sè siōng-kài cheng-chháu ê piàn-tōa siōng-kài cheng-chháu.

question: 2003 ni chu 2005 ni 'net loss as reported' kap 'pro-forma net loss' tiong-kan ū sím-iáⁿ koan-hē?
answer: Chiah-ê koan-hē sī ti̍t-chiap kap tēⁿ-chhiat ê, múi chi̍t nî ê 'pro-forma net loss' lóng pí 'net loss as reported' koh-khah tōa (tōa hāu-bī). Saⁿ nî ê nn̄g ê kiàⁿ-bo̍k lóng chiap-chhiap-tek piáu-sī chhián-tiāⁿ (sún-sit tiâu-chhiáⁿ) ê kòng-tō͘, chiū-kóng thàu-kòe kiàⁿ-bo̍k ê chè-tō͘ lâi kóng, chiàⁿ-chún ê sū-bū chiàⁿ-thâu sī ū kiàⁿ-bo̍k ê só͘-ū piàn-tōng ê ki-pún kiâⁿ-thâu.

question: Bie tioh tioh 325321 ê khòaⁿ, oân-á chòe-chiàⁿ khòaⁿ, kap 'add' kap 'less' hāng-mū, chiah ē tit-tioh 'pro-forma net loss'? Chhèng 2003 nî ê chhit-gia̍h lâi kiám-chèng.
answer: Jī-hō͘ sī: ('net loss as reported') + ('add : stock-based employee compensation expense net of related tax effect included in net loss as reported') - ('less : total stock-based employee compensation expense determined under fair value based method for all awards net of related taxeffect'). Chheh 2003 nî ê chhit-gia̍h lâi kóng: (-325321) + (2077) - (31156) = -354400, chiap-chhiap tioh hit nî ê 'pro-forma net loss'.

question: 2003 ni sun-kàu 2005 ni, lān-chiáⁿ hō͘ pò-kò ê lān-chiáⁿ tī-tīnn-á piàn-tò͘?
answer: 2003 ni ê lān-chiáⁿ hō͘ pò-kò ê lān-chiáⁿ tùi $325,321 kàu 2005 ni ê $171,590 kòe-tō͘.
